@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At <strong>Aeronexa</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting
    your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and
    safeguard your data when you use our airline ticket booking system.
</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Personal details such as name, email address, and contact information</li>
    <li>Passenger information required for flight bookings</li>
    <li>Booking and reservation details</li>
    <li>Payment-related information (only for transaction processing)</li>
</ul>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<ul>
    <li>To process flight bookings and reservations</li>
    <li>To generate e-tickets and booking confirmations</li>
    <li>To send booking-related emails and notifications</li>
    <li>To improve system performance and user experience</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>
    Aeronexa uses secure authentication and authorization mechanisms to protect
    user data. Access to sensitive information is restricted and managed through
    role-based authorization.
</p>

<h3>Data Sharing</h3>
<p>
    We do not share your personal information with third parties except when
    required for payment processing or by law.
</p>

<h3>Your Consent</h3>
<p>
    By using the Aeronexa system, you agree to the collection and use of information
    as described in this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
<p>
    Aeronexa may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
    reflected on this page.
</p>

<p class="mt-4">
    If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact the
    Aeronexa support team.
</p>
